{"tid":1563974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大合唱令場運動走向失敗?","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:52.000Z","uid":321572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae59001d78796c57d58edb4533038f85192094c7","tid":1563974,"uid":321572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"P牌仔表示見到連登最近多左post話最近搞嘅各區大合唱, 同雨革唱今天我一樣會令場運動走向失敗, 有少少睇法<br />\n<br />\n++) 各區大合唱, 除左吸引媒體關注, 唱屬於香港人嘅國歌係能夠好強咁增加大家嘅歸屬感, 就好似打機蓄氣出招咁, 下下攻唔蓄氣又點掂? <br />\n眼見連一D老一輩都攞住紙仔努力背用力唱, 成件事係超感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--) 感動完, 理性D 諗各區大合唱凝聚到社區嘅民氣, 但有冇充份利用到集結到嘅力量?<br />\nP牌仔係和理非, 唔鼓勵衝擊, 但唔衝擊又有咩方法去幫到呢場運動? 其實根本好多post 都有答案:<br />\n全港性-連儂牆修復行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1560793/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1560793/page/1</a><br />\n[長文] [經濟戰] 罷買/最低消費攻略方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1437510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1437510/page/1</a><br />\n最新抵制清單 (修改版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1472004/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1472004/page/1</a><br />\n【網上戰線】我地要打好輿論戰！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1275647/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1275647/page/1</a><br />\n認真請大家關注白宮聯署！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1178028/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1178028/page/1</a><br />\n.........<br />\n<br />\n但係點解冇咩聲氣???<br />\n<br />\n終於知點解無人再貼文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563663/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><em>因為有D人仲未了解呢D行動?<br />\n因為覺得出席完唱完已經付出左?<br />\n因為一個人/少人淆底?</em></em><br />\n<br />\n其實好多人都係受羊群效應影響,只要身邊其他人都做,自自然然就唔會淆<br />\n<strong>集結到一群人而唔好好利用係好浪費</strong>,正如打機蓄完氣唔出招,咁蓄黎做咩? <br />\n<br />\nP牌仔冇咩大計, 因為大計好多巴絲打已經獻左, 只係我地需要將D 行動連結<br />\n各區大合唱完, 可唔可以帶隊去修復連儂牆? 搞手會可唔可以幫手<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">宣傳罷買</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span></span>/<span style=\"color: green;\">聯署</span>/<span style=\"color: purple;\">網上戰</span>(<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">即場鼓勵人port藍絲page 咩都好)</span></span>/<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捐款(e.g. 星火)</span></span>? </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人其實已經connect左, 只係點樣將人connect 去我地嘅行動, 否則可能真係同雨革唱今天我一樣會走向失敗....."},{"pid":"16fe3eb0ef914e661817f9ad749bed86ffb00c4a","tid":1563974,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:02:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74